ISLAMABAD, Feb 25 (APP): Minister for Information and Broadcasting Marriyum Aurangzeb on Saturday shared Pakistan Tehreek-e-Insaf Chairman Imran Khan’s anti-judiciary speeches on social media to expose his hypocrisy.
She, in a tweet, termed Imran Khan “Munafaq-e-Azam”. The tweet also included a video clip showing his rants against the judiciary on different occasions.
